headline: Real American Beer & WWE Debut Limited-Edition "Hulkamania Forever" Light Beer
summary: TAMPA, Fla., September 23, 2025--This fall, Hulkamania takes over the beer aisle. Real American Beer (RAB) will launch Hulkamania Forever, a 16oz limited-edition beer created in partnership with WWE that celebrates the legacy of WWE Hall of Famer Hulk Hogan. The can made its global debut Saturday night in front of a sold-out crowd at WWE Wrestlepalooza in Indianapolis.
